<DOCNO> LA041894-0044 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 033313 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 18, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 1; Column 1; Financial Desk 
